<br>
Meeting spot is in Burning Woods at the DL zone.  We will be moving out no later than 7:15p PST so if you are late, it is your responsibility to catch up.  In order to get the most out of our time, we must stick to the schedule so please make arrangements to camp in meeting spot the night before, log in early, etc.  <br>
<br>
I strongly suggest you print a map so that if you get separated from the group when making the run towards Sarnak Fort and Chardok, you are able to continue.  We CANNOT stop for everybody that gets lost.  At these levels, people need to know how to use their loc and sense heading and know how to navigate through a zone.  If you need a guide, hire one as this is not a tour of the world according to you.<br>
<br>
&lt;b&gt;The raid tactics are a MUST READ for this zone.&lt;/b&gt;  We do not want to lose our clerics or enchanters because someone was unfamiliar with the tactics.  There will be an MA, you will be required to use your assist appropriately, know when to engage a mob, when to stop attacking, when to heal, who to heal, how to handle adds, how to attack the mobs based on proven raid tactics that work, how loot will be dealt with, etc.  &lt;b&gt;PLEASE TAKE A MOMENT NOW TO READ THE RAID TACTICS.&lt;/b&gt;  There is a link in this forum (Raids/Events).  <br>
<br>
This is VERY IMPORTANT... If you make three (3) mistakes that are clearly in violation of the posted raid tactics, you will be removed from group and asked to leave for the remainder of the raid.   Using incorrect tactics or not paying attention to commands endangers the group(s) and those fighting around you.  <br>
<br>
In order to speed up the planning for this raid, please reply here with your class and level if you will be attending.  This is an open raid. FoJ and LoW are invited to attend.  <br>
<br>
Our goal is to become familiar with the zone, the mobs that are there and the raid tactics needed for this dungeon.<br>
<br>
If there are any questions or suggestions. please post a reply here as well.<br>
<br>
Thanks!<br>
<br>
